279
00:27:29,564 --> 00:27:30,898
Dank je.

280
00:28:50,562 --> 00:28:51,812
Nee.

281
00:28:51,896 --> 00:28:53,647
Overnieuw weer.

282
00:29:18,673 --> 00:29:21,091
Okay. Dat is genoeg, alsjeblieft.

283
00:29:21,885 --> 00:29:23,802
Je doet het te snel.

284
