319
00:32:54,639 --> 00:32:55,722
Wat?

320
00:32:55,807 --> 00:32:57,391
Mam, dit ben jij.

321
00:32:57,475 --> 00:32:59,893
"Oh, heerlijk,
Dit ijs is zo lekker hier,

322
